title: The Strongest Unemployed Hero
description: The Strongest Unemployed Hero Manhwa Shin min-cheol had been recruited to the world called ‘anhelles’. He was one who had lived 200 years fighting to survival and destroying the enemies, in the end the ruler of the continent Zero, was lead to the victory of war. And finally, Min-cheol, who has finally returned to Earth leaving the peace of anhelles behind, wants to live his long-awaited life as a ‘rich unemployed man’, but another conspiracy begins to approach him? If they are after me, they have to find me first. All I have to do is go and fight it off! The Strongest Unemployed Hero 백수무적 Jobless, Yet Invincible The Invincible Deadbeat
